{"tid":435558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長者不滿巴士站無斜台自己動手起 遭工聯會議員阻止","createTime":"2017-10-14T11:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T12:30:18.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d8c896e0dc034704d29b67f6e675f20dd1f1d0","tid":435558,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57332026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57332026&d=qhykyEhMnRht1cruuPfc5TM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=58074595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171014%2F57332026&h=e9233c54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171014/57332026</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171014/large/1507979686_e857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171014%2Flarge%2F1507979686_e857.jpg&h=39c5a776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有市民發現，今日下午有人於筲箕灣東熹苑巴士站，自行帶建築材料到場興建斜台，質疑僭建斜台會影響埋站巴士安全，有人更認出工聯會東區區議員許林慶亦同時在場。<br />\n<br />\n許林慶接受本報查詢時稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">當時一名興東邨女長者街坊，因不滿附近欠缺行人過路及無障礙設施，「佢鬧政府唔做嘢」，一怒之下買齊英泥等材料，今日下午到巴士站位置，自行興建斜台，希望方便輪椅人士上落。</span><br />\n<br />\n許林慶說，他收到消息後，已即時到現場勸阻婆婆停止建斜台工程，終說服婆婆停止再施工，並向婆婆承諾，會將婆婆希望興建斜台告知運輸署。他指，現場最接近的斜台，在巴士站外100多米位置，街坊如要從興東邨出發走到該巴士站，需要步行接近300米，相當不方便。<span style=\"color: red;\">他稱，會盡快通知運輸署協助清走水泥，並促當局考慮在合適地點</span>，設無障礙過路設施方便居民。"},{"pid":"f0339ed0db185ed82719e4c98c78cb03b74e0261","tid":435558,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505140f6b3220729888685a6311b61